snippet.title: Assault Suit Leynos - Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
http://www.risingstargames.com/eu/games/assault-suit-leynos/

A classic reawakens – Assault Suit Leynos is back and in high definition! Get ready for all-out robotic war as the fan-favorite Mega Drive classic is reworked with all new HD visuals for the ultimate alien-blasting experience!
